    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Office File",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "TO : Director, FBI",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "FROM : Legal Attache, Havana, Cuba",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "SUBJECT: REPORTS OF FLYING DISCS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "FOREIGN MISCELLANEOUS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "The following information is submitted as of interest",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "to the Bureau in the event reports of flying discs are still desired.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "The Havana daily newspaper \"Diario de la Marina\" November 12,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "1957, carried a dispatch dated November 11, 1957, at Pinar del Rio,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "Cuba, reporting that [REDACTED] and [REDACTED] who had",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "just arrived in that town from the Matahambre Mines in Pinar del Rio",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Province, claimed that they had seen a flying disc in the shape of a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "man's hat hovering over the general area of Matahambre for several",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "minutes. They claimed that this disc was larger than ordinary airplanes",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "normally seen in that area and that it was completely silent in its",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "flight. They said that it disappeared at a very high speed towards",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "the sea. There was no further descriptive information furnished in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "this newspaper article. It is noted that Matahambre is located",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "approximately 90 miles to the west of Havana. No other reports",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "corroborating the above were received and no inquiry has been made",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "by this office.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
